    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/a9c0c7e5c9ce0dbbbe066b3e0b0b02c9.webp?t=1769069140\" width=500 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/64e5608514eb60a7d7733592510e42fa.avif?t=1769069140\" width=1000 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/b8f3d332c9ac91d10e6e0a6350c6dc0d.avif?t=1769069140\" width=800 height=941 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>所有男性都已从地球上消失，迎来了全新的世界黎明。</strong><br><strong>在这个仅有女性生存的末世之中，一场宏大而神秘的史诗即将展开。</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/64b485328ba1f52dc470be826473408c.poster.avif?t=1769069140\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/64b485328ba1f52dc470be826473408c.webm?t=1769069140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>在唯一真神 La 的祝福下，男性于1500年前从这个世界消失。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这完美的和平之中，由拥有超能力者组成的特种部队“Eclipse”一直守护着世界的秩序与安定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/6ac6690801b232d45f80d9444d5046ba.poster.avif?t=1769069140\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/6ac6690801b232d45f80d9444d5046ba.webm?t=1769069140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，随着新兴宗教团体“阿佩普”的崛起，隐藏的裂痕开始浮现。<br>身为“Eclipse”成员的<strong>Haesu</strong>被卷入命运的漩涡，<br>而她一直深信不疑的和平背后，却隐藏着被遗忘的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最终，命运的齿轮开始转动。<br><strong>Haesu</strong>将做出怎样的选择？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/b69b20287761226e1e4321a2086d739c.poster.avif?t=1769069140\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/b69b20287761226e1e4321a2086d739c.webm?t=1769069140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>一切，皆掌握在你的手中。<br>与<strong>Haesu</strong>一同揭开“Eclipse”世界的秘密，直面潜藏的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>互动式视觉小说：多重结局系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/45a1b582dc45d73592c5d35f9d2f448c.poster.avif?t=1769069140\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/45a1b582dc45d73592c5d35f9d2f448c.webm?t=1769069140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/77facc9d64a24b6c0fa40b051c827ada.poster.avif?t=1769069140\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/77facc9d64a24b6c0fa40b051c827ada.webm?t=1769069140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏根据玩家的选择设有分支点，让玩家在推进故事的过程中体验不同的事件和结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的选择将决定故事的发展方向，主角也将因此迎来截然不同的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>时间攻击机制：选择还是命运？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/6f48aafd833a0abf8b10c2e64251953e.poster.avif?t=1769069140\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/6f48aafd833a0abf8b10c2e64251953e.webm?t=1769069140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong></strong><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>在关键时刻，Time Attack 条将出现——迅速抉择，否则后果自负。<br>你会相信自己作为 Eclipse 特战队员的洞察力，还是听命于命运？由你决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>视觉概念：漫画风格</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/ba22bc7e98f4065fb109dbe1361a89d3.poster.avif?t=1769069140\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/ba22bc7e98f4065fb109dbe1361a89d3.webm?t=1769069140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/1f076cf33502660691ead71e366d115b.poster.avif?t=1769069140\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/1f076cf33502660691ead71e366d115b.webm?t=1769069140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的主要事件场景采用漫画风格呈现，让玩家仿佛翻阅漫画书般，感受其独特的乐趣与怀旧氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/3d0b555d593127532ecfbfa7e852a884.avif?t=1769069140\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共计124张精美插图与生动的漫画风格表现，极大提升沉浸感</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>世界观: #埃及神话 #超能力 #军事 #末世废土</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Eclipse》的世界观以古埃及神话为灵感，构筑了一个独特的舞台。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这片瑰丽的末世之中，超能力与军事力量交织，共同编织出一场震撼人心的史诗。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>角色介绍:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/6e82601a0343e47cdca049250637248e.poster.avif?t=1769069140\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/6e82601a0343e47cdca049250637248e.webm?t=1769069140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真的，讲真——从头到尾只有女性角色，一个接一个，全都是女性。这就是我们的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/486f3f36e26c4c52567a6fdeec9e8483.avif?t=1769069140\" width=510 height=510 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Haesu（《Eclipse》的主角）</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「嗯，好吧。那就把这地方翻个底朝天吧。」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eclipse成员 / 异能无效化</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然<strong>Haesu</strong>自认为自己并没有强烈的正义感，但在她人眼中却截然不同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她那无法忽视她人困境的本能，让她被众人称为“天生的多管闲事者”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在调查“无差别恐怖袭击事件”的过程中，她逐渐接近一个令人震惊的真相，并站在了命运的十字路口……？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/aaa11b247f9cafe03b95b8b76fdb02b6.avif?t=1769069140\" width=510 height=510 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dallae</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“我宁愿死，也不愿输。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eclipse成员 / 幻觉操控</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Haesu</strong>的搭档，曾揭开无差别恐怖袭击事件背后的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于自幼以来建立的特殊羁绊，她对<strong>Haesu</strong>格外重视。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，对其她人却始终冷漠，甚至经常表现得极为冷酷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/113c758db99c2dd51bba58a8abae3e33.avif?t=1769069140\" width=510 height=510 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>先知</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eclipse总指挥官</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“我唯一的选择就是带着罪孽生存，并将我的罪行毫无保留地呈献给伟大的母亲。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为唯一能听见万物创造者La之声的人，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她被世人尊崇，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并被奉为太阳神的代言人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/4b2db6c6828d1d488db65558da465284.avif?t=1769069140\" width=510 height=510 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>反派A</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“愿神的祝福与你同在。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>Haesu</strong>和<strong>Dallae</strong>卧底调查时，她主持了一场仅限精英参加的聚会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她所佩戴的山羊面具，象征着邪恶，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为她的存在增添了一种诡异且令人不安的气息。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/1955cb61931b8c7c6beaa9847cf3437c.avif?t=1769069140\" width=510 height=510 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>反派B</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“知道也没有意义，反正你马上就要死了。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她完全听从A的指令行事，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >姓名、年龄、过去，甚至一切身份信息都笼罩在神秘之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/d09ef14ca0d32fffe5cdc3374222a79b.avif?t=1769069140\" width=510 height=510 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>反派C</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“对于那些短暂而卑微地活着的人……我将赐予你们永恒的地狱。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她对太阳信仰（Solarism）和Eclipse怀有极深的敌意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凭借强大的超自然能力，她引领着追随者前行，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而她所踏足之处，只留下漆黑死寂的虚无。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>试玩版可体验的系统与功能</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在试玩版中，您可以游玩 <strong>序章部分的内容</strong>。<br> <strong>除相册功能外，所有系统功能均可使用。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>试玩版内容概览：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共85个章节中的 <strong>8个章节</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共28个选项中的 <strong>4个可体验</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共51个场景中的 <strong>4个场景</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共124张CG中的 <strong>10张CG</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam总计59项成就中的 <strong>5项可解锁</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎踏上属于你的日之旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>试玩版支持4种语言！（韩语/English/简体中文/日本語）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本次试玩版的翻译承蒙AI翻译的协助，如有不足之处，敬请海涵，并恳请您的理解与包容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>※此页面和游戏的翻译由 AI 协助完成。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✹由专业译者打造的正统英文本地化。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290520/extras/536c419844f70a646a5f3b8786d45799.avif?t=1769069140\" width=800 height=471 /></span></p>",
